<div id="review_2104687246" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2104687246" />
    <a title="Mehrsa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1045774-mehrsa"><img alt="Mehrsa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1218672696p2/1045774.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2104687246?book_show_action=true">Aug 26, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mehrsa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mehrsa" href="/user/show/1045774-mehrsa">Mehrsa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2104687246" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4708370904500091409">Essential reading that has not aged at all. There was so much here--commentary, history, and well written analysis of current events. Though the current events are now history, it was still totally relevant. This is a must read. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


