<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/12390008-the-reactionary-mind"><img alt="The Reactionary Mind: Conservatism from Edmund Burke to Sarah Palin" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348049597l/12390008._SX98_.jpg" />
